#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/weka.rst:9
msgid ""
"WekaFS is a high-performance, distributed filesystem and is a supported "
"option for KV Cache offloading in LMCache. Even though the local "
"filesystem backend can work with a WekaFS mount, this particular backend "
"is optimized for Weka's characteristics. It leverages GPUDirect Storage "
"for I/O and it allows data-sharing between multiple LMCache instances."
msgstr ""

